import React from 'react'
import {
  Drawer,
  DrawerBody,
  DrawerFooter,
  DrawerHeader,
  DrawerOverlay,
  DrawerContent,
  DrawerCloseButton,
  useDisclosure,
  Flex, Box, Spacer, Text, Stack, Radio, RadioGroup, CheckboxGroup, Checkbox,
} from "@chakra-ui/react"
import ProductCustomizationDrawer from '../Container/ProductCustomizationDrawer/ProductCustomizationDrawer'
import _ from "lodash";
const ViewDrawer = () => {
  const data=[
    {id:1,type:'radio',name:'Extra Cheese',customisationTag:'SELECT ANY ONE'},
    {id:1,type:'radio',name:'Extra Cheese',customisationTag:'SELECT ANY ONE'},
    {id:1,type:'checkbox',name:'Extra Cheese',customisationTag:'SELECT EXTRAS'},
    {id:1,type:'checkbox',name:'Extra Cheese',customisationTag:'SELECT EXTRAS'},
    {id:1,type:'radio',name:'Extra Cheese',customisationTag:'SELECT ANY ONE'},
    {id:1,type:'radio',name:'Extra Cheese',customisationTag:'SELECT ANY ONE'},
  ]
  let groupData = _.groupBy(data, "customisationTag");
  console.log(groupData,"groupData")
  return (
    <>
  
    <ProductCustomizationDrawer>
       {Object.keys(groupData).map((customisationTag,index)=>{
          console.log(customisationTag,"customisationTag")
         return(
            <Box>
            <Text my="25px" fontWeight="extrabold">{customisationTag}</Text>
            <RadioGroup defaultValue="1">
              <Stack>
                <Radio value="1" colorScheme="green"><Text>Checked</Text> </Radio>
                <Radio value="2" colorScheme="green"><Text>Unchecked</Text></Radio>
                <Radio value="3" colorScheme="green"><Text>Unchecked</Text></Radio>
              </Stack>
            </RadioGroup>
          </Box>
          )
       })}
      </ProductCustomizationDrawer>
    </>
  )
}

export default ViewDrawer
